sentences: Mohammed ibn Mohammed ibn Musa ibn Mohammed al-Sharqi al-Sumayli ibn Tayyib al-Fasi al-Alami (Arabic: ابن الطيب الشرقي; 1698-1756) was a famous Moroccan linguist, historian and scholar of fikh (law) and hadith.
Uyun al-Mawarid al-Salsalah min Uyun al-Asanid al-Musalsalah
al-lstisha bima fi dhat al-Shifa fi Sirah al-Nabi- thumma al Khulafa
Maalayhi al-Maul min Mabahith al-Sayyid al-Matuf
